Package suncertify.db

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DB
    Interface provided by instructions
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Data
    Implementation of DB interface supplied by the instructions.
    DBAccess
    Used to interact with the Database on the physical file system.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DatabaseInitializationException
    An exception we throw when there is a problem with initializing the DB.
    DuplicateKeyException
    Exits just to fulfill the interface requirements.
    RecordNotFoundException
    Any time the user requests record 'x' for updating, deleting or just reading and record 'x' Either does not exist or has been flagged as deleted then we throw this exception
    SecurityException
    We throw this exception when the lock cookie supplied does not match the Lock cookie that is currently holding the lock on a record
